---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="About | Electrical Engineering Portfolio" description="Background, experience, and approach to electrical engineering work.">
	<section class="container about-page">
		<header>
			<h1>About Me</h1>
			<p>
				I'm an electrical engineer who loves building reliable systems - starting from whiteboard concepts
				and landing with hardware that performs in the field. I thrive at the intersection of electronics,
				firmware, and data where thoughtful instrumentation unlocks measurable outcomes.
			</p>
		</header>

		<section>
			<div class="section-heading">
				<h2>Principles</h2>
				<span>How I work</span>
			</div>
			<ul class="about-list">
				<li>
					<strong>Design for the environment.</strong> Requirements mean nothing if a device can't survive
					where it lives. I qualify early, budget power with margin, and validate across extremes.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Firmware &amp; hardware together.</strong> I write firmware that understands the hardware and
					vice versa. That feedback loop keeps integration smooth and debugging actionable.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Evidence over intuition.</strong> Instrument everything. Measure. Let the data drive
					decisions on architecture, component selection, and optimization work.
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<div class="section-heading">
				<h2>Experience</h2>
				<span>Selected Roles</span>
			</div>
			<ul class="timeline">
				<li>
					<strong>Principal Electrical Engineer</strong> - GridSense Labs (2022-Present)
					<p>
						Leading hardware for distributed energy platforms, from power electronics to OTA firmware
						deliveries and data infrastructure.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Senior Embedded Engineer</strong> - MotionCraft (2019-2022)
					<p>
						Architected mixed-signal control systems for inspection robotics with custom sensing,
						precision actuators, and deterministic firmware.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Electrical Engineer</strong> - FieldLabs (2016-2019)
					<p>
						Designed rugged IoT hardware, telemetry backhauls, and field automation for agriculture and
						environmental impact projects.
					</p>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<div class="section-heading">
				<h2>Stack</h2>
				<span>Toolbox</span>
			</div>
			<div class="tag-cloud">
				<span>KiCad</span>
				<span>Altium</span>
				<span>LTspice</span>
				<span>MATLAB</span>
				<span>STM32</span>
				<span>ESP-IDF</span>
				<span>FreeRTOS</span>
				<span>Zephyr</span>
				<span>Rust</span>
				<span>Python</span>
				<span>FPGA</span>
				<span>JTAG</span>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="contact-card">
			<h2>Let's collaborate</h2>
			<p>
				I'm always open to interesting challenges - especially ones involving energy, mission critical hardware,
				or instrumentation in demanding environments.
			</p>
			<div class="hero-actions">
				<a class="button primary" href="mailto:you@example.com">Start a conversation</a>
				<a class="button secondary" href={`${base}projects`}>View my work</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-page {
		display: grid;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.about-page header {
		background: var(--color-card);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.16);
		padding: 2.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
	}

	.about-page header h1 {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.about-page header p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		max-width: 70ch;
	}

	.about-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: grid;
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	.about-list li {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.82);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.14);
		color: var(--color-muted);
	}

	.about-list strong {
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.01em;
	}

	.timeline {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: grid;
		gap: 1.75rem;
	}

	.timeline li {
		padding: 1.75rem;
		border-left: 3px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
		background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.78);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	.timeline strong {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.01em;
	}

	.timeline p {
		margin: 0.65rem 0 0;
		color: var(--color-muted);
	}

	.tag-cloud {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.tag-cloud span {
		padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.14);
		color: var(--color-muted);
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
	}

	.contact-card {
		padding: 2.5rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12), rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08));
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.16);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
	}

	.contact-card h2 {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		font-size: 2rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.015em;
	}

	.contact-card p {
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		max-width: 60ch;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.about-page header,
		.about-list li,
		.timeline li,
		.contact-card {
			padding: 1.75rem;
		}
	}
</style>
